Deg wass n [[1 fuṛaṛ]] [[2022]], yeɣli ugrud [[Ṛayan Awṛam]] (ilan 5 n yiseggasen, si [[Ameṛṛuk|Tgelda n Umeṛṛuk]]) deg yiwen n wanu yekkawen, tilqi-ines 32 m<ref>{{Cite web|title=A boy fell 100 feet down a well days ago. The world is watching, hoping to #SaveRayan|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2022/02/04/boy-trapped-morocco-well-save-rayan/6661278001/|access-date=2022-02-06|website=USA TODAY|language=en-US}}</ref> di taddart n [[Iɣran]] yeṭṭafaren taɣiwant n [[Tamurut|tmurut]] deg [[Agezdu n Accawen|ugezdu n Accawen]] i d-yezgan deg ugafa n [[Ameṛṛuk|Umeṛṛuk]]. Tamsalt-is d tkesna-ines tla-d (tesɛa-d) yiwet n txitert d umisi meqren deg umaḍal yakk, anda imelyan n yimdanen deg yakk ideggan n umaḍal zgan ṭṭafaren tamhelt n usellek-ines deg tansiwin n tmetti (Facebook, YouTube, twitter...) d tregwa n yisalan n tiliẓri neɣ ṛadyu.
Ɣef teɣzi n 5 n wussan, llan-d warramen meqren i wakken ad ssufɣen Ṛayan seg wanu, maca ur ssawḍen ara alammi d ass n [[5 fuṛaṛ]]. Maca ufan-t yemmut. 
