== Tamhelt n usellek ==
Di tmeddit n wass n [[sad]] [[5 fuṛaṛ]], telɣet-d tnarit tageldant n Umeṛṛuk ɣef tmettant n Ṛayan s usrag (sebba) n [[tiggest|tiggas]] s wacu i d-yegla uɣelluy-ines s agensu n wanu send n 5 n wussan. Imir-nni ya, agellid [[Muḥemmed wis 6]] yessawel i bab-as d yimma-as n Ṛayan i wakken ad ten-yefced (ad ten-iɛzzi).
